item.title: The Classics Episode 2: Monkeys Don't Exist
item.itunes:title: The Classics: Monkeys Don't Exist
item.description:
A crazy duel, a man makes the grossest sacrifice for God, and a crazy man believes in all sorts of crazy things. Namely, that monkeys don't exist.

 

In 2005, a man killed his mother and spent 8 hours skinning her body. And that's not even the weirdest part.

 

Then we look at "Conspiracies by Hans," a Youtube channel that believes volcanos and monkeys don't exist, most people are the opposite sex than they appear, and the color orange is evil. Yeah, it gets weird.
